pro_course_detail.description:
Dear Russian Language learners!

If you are going to Russia as a tourist or to visit your Russian relatives, or you are starting to work in Russia I am happy to offer you a 10-lesson course after completing which you will be able to:
*talk about yourself (name, job, hobbies);
*use common verbs in all three tenses (present, future and past);
*use greetings;
*ask for help;
*communicate in the hotel, airport, restaurant, in the supermarket
*read signs in the city, announcements, ads.

Spasibo! 
See you on my lessons!

- general conversation practice on every-day-topics;
- exercises to improve pronunciation;
- speaking practice on topics related to the Russian culture;
- homework is not included.

- a focus on grammar constructions, difficult cases in the Russian grammar;
- grammar excercises and writing practice;
- homework is provided, but not checked.

