teacher_info.teaching_style:
We will ...
✓ create the INDIVIDUAL study PLAN based on your goals and interests;
✓ enrich your vocabulary by READING the most interesting for you books and articles;
✓ improve your LISTENING and PRONUNCIATION skills by listening to podcasts, interviews, and songs;
✓ TALK about different topics so you can express your thoughts freely and sound fluent;
✓ learn GRAMMAR from the context; 
✓ use interactive tools (Quizlet) to help you memorize information better;
✓ REVIEW what you have learned so you won't forget the material we studied together.

