This course is for you if ...
- you want to learn the vocabulary for communicating with people in Ukraine in the most common situations (get to know each other - order in the restaurant - buy the tickets - visit the shop...);
- you are interested in Ukrainian culture and would like to know more about it;
- want to understand how Ukrainian grammar works;
- want to be able to talk about your interests, share your thoughts, and maintain the conversation.

