This course is for you if you want... 
- to speak English confidently; 
- to enlarge vocabulary and memorize new words using them in conversation; 
- to learn new grammar from the context;
- to improve your listening and writing skills.

Every lesson has a different topic, according to the course that I`ll design specifically for you. And all material corresponds to your level of English and goal (for travels, for yourself, for work).

I am looking forward to our meeting!

Let`s learn Ukrainian in the most unusual way!

Together we will listen to the most popular Ukrainian bands and singers (The Hardkiss, Kalush Orchestra, Go-A, Один в каное, Vivienne Mort...) and ... 
1) boost your vocabulary by discussing the meaning of the lyrics; 
2) learn new grammar finding the most interesting structures in the songs; 
3) develop your conversational skills talking about the artists and their art.

I can`t wait to meet you!
